Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:28.00,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}Death sickleが指揮者ね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:31.55,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}魅惑のレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:35.19,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}突き刺さる心の十字架に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:38.80,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}何を誓って戯れようか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:40.88,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}焦らした指先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.70,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}先駆けた誘惑の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:46.73,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}糸を手繰って すぐココに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.60,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}心から溢れ出した
